Privacy Policy:

24/7 Casino is referred to as "Bot"

By using this Bot you're agreeing to the Privacy Policy.

The use of this Bot requires you to give us some Data. This data includes Discord user Ids. Use of the Bot is considered an agreement to the Privacy Policy.

Access to Data:

All of the Discord user IDs are stored in an aiosqlite database. Only the Bot owner (Goated#2235) has access to the database. This database is secured to prevent access of those who aren't allowed to access it. If there is a breach of data, it will be posted on the support server. https://discord.gg/nXjzVHe2Ez

User Rights

At any time, you're allowed to request us to view the Data we have pertaining to your discord account.

Underage Users

The use of this Bot is not permitted for users under the age of 13 or legal consent for their country. We will not knowingly store any data from an underage user. If we find out a user is underage we will take all necessary actions to remove this data.

Tracking of user Message

We track all of user messages if the bot is in the server, this will allow users to talk to earn money. You may opt out of this feature, unless if you opt out messages will be stored in the ram and we will not access your messages or your read them for any reasons.

